Flux 
=======

Flux....

Need mongodb installed, 
with a DB called flux

Installation 
------------

client (from repo directory)

# cd flux
# bower install
======= 
server  (from repo directory)

# cd flux.server
# npm install


Start the bouzin
------------
# cd flux.server
# node app.js (or, to watch directory use: npm start)



routes
------------

http://localhost:8080/connector
Connect account to different social accounts
and save feeds to DB

http://localhost:8080/
launch once 
